    • Student

      public Student(String studentName, String studentAddress, String studentPhoneNo, String studentEmail)
      Constructs a Student instance with the specified name, address, phone number, and email.
      Parameters:
      studentName - the name of the student, as a non-null, non-empty String
      studentAddress - the address of the student, as a non-null, non-empty String
      studentPhoneNo - the phone number of the student, as a non-null String
      studentEmail - the email of the student, as a non-null String
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if studentName, studentAddress, studentPhoneNo, or studentEmail is null or empty
